                  </mech>  
                  <list1> 
                    <l1item> 
                      <para>Check of the Pressure.</para>  
                      <para lang="zh">压力检查</para>  
                      <para> 
                        <grphcref refid="en52100099104400003" shownow="0">Door-Damper and Emergency-Operation Cylinder Figure 52-10-00-991-04400-00-C / SHEET 1</grphcref> 
                      </para>  
                      <list2> 
                        <l2item> 
                          <caution> 
                            <para>THE PRESSURE ON THE PRESSURE INDICATOR OF THE BOTTLE MUST BE RELATED TO THE PRESSURE CORRECTED FOR TEMPERATURE.</para> 
                          </caution>  
                          <caution-zh> 
                            <para>蓄压瓶压力表指示值应涉及到温度校正压力值。</para> 
                          </caution-zh>  
                          <para>Make sure that the door is open.</para>  
                          <para>确认舱门已打开。</para> 
                        </l2item>  
                        <l2item> 
                          <para>Read and record the pressure value shown on the pressure gauge (1).</para>  
                          <para>读出并记录下压力表（1）指示压力值。</para>  
                          <table> 
                            <tgroup cols="4"> <?PubTbl tgroup dispwid="683.00px"?>
  
                              <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.00*"/>  
                              <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.00*"/>  
                              <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.00*"/>  
                              <colspec colname="col4" colwidth="0.99*"/>  
                              <tbody> 
                                <row> 
                                  <entry morerows="1"/>  
                                  <entry namest="col2" nameend="col3"> 
                                    <para>检查结果（Inspection result）</para> 
                                  </entry>  
                                  <entry morerows="1"> 
                                    <para>处理方法 Performing procedure</para> 
                                  </entry> 
                                </row>  
                                <row> 
                                  <entry> 
                                    <para>环境温度 ambient temp</para> 
                                  </entry>  
                                  <entry> 
                                    <para>压力值 pressure value</para> 
                                  </entry> 
                                </row>  
                                <row> 
                                  <entry> 
                                    <para>左前门 LH FWD DOOR</para> 
                                  </entry>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry> 
                                    <sign id="sign53989"> 
                                      <mech authid="B201117" authname="A320-214机型航线维护（限制项目）" ispreparation="N" display="N"> 
                                        <mechname> 
                                          <input/> 
                                        </mechname>  
                                        <mechdate> 
                                          <input/> 
                                        </mechdate> 
                                      </mech> 
                                    </sign> 
                                  </entry> 
                                </row>  
                                <row> 
                                  <entry> 
                                    <para>左后门 LH REAR DOOR</para> 
                                  </entry>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/> 
                                </row>  
                                <row> 
                                  <entry> 
                                    <para>右前门 RH FWD DOOR</para> 
                                  </entry>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/> 
                                </row>  
                                <row> 
                                  <entry> 
                                    <para>右后门 RH REAR DOOR</para> 
                                  </entry>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/>  
                                  <entry/> 
                                </row> 
                              </tbody> 
                            </tgroup> 
                          </table>  
                          <list3> 
                            <l3item> 
                              <para>Compare this value with the value on the placard (2) for the ambient temperature.</para>  
                              <para>将该记录值与标牌（2）上相应环境温度下的标准值相比较。</para>  
                              <note> 
                                <para>Let the air bottle become stable at the ambient temperature before you do the inspection. This is to get a correct pressure value.</para> 
                              </note>  
                              <note-zh> 
                                <para>让蓄压瓶稳定到环境温度，再检查压力值，这样可获得准确的压力值。</para> 
                              </note-zh> 
                            </l3item> 
                          </list3> 
                        </l2item>  
                        <l2item> 
                          <para>If the pressure is not correct, charge the cylinder bottle.
                            <refblock>52-10-00-614-001 
                              <refint refid="en52100061400100"> 
                                <effect effrg="001999"/>52-10-00-614-001-A
                              </refint> 
                            </refblock> 
                          </para>  
                          <para lang="zh">如果压力值不足，向蓄压瓶充气。 
                            <refblock>52-10-00-614-001 
                              <refint refid="en52100061400100"> 
                                <effect effrg="001999"/>52-10-00-614-001-A
                              </refint> 
                            </refblock> 
                          </para> 
                        </l2item> 
                      </list2> 
                    </l1item> 
                  </list1> 
                </sign> 
              </subtask> 
