                  <list1> 
                    <l1item> 
                      <para>Close Access</para>  
                      <para>关闭接近</para>  
                      <list2> 
                        <l2item> 
                          <para>Make sure that the work area is clean and clear of tools and other items.</para>  
                          <para>确认工作区域应清洁，无工具和其它外来物。</para> 
                        </l2item>  
                        <l2item> 
                          <para>Obey the special precautions after the work on the door 
                            <refblock>52-10-00-860-002 
                              <refint refid="en52100086000200"> 
                                <effect effrg="001999"/>52-10-00-860-002-A
                              </refint> 
                            </refblock>.
                          </para>  
                          <para lang="zh">完成舱门工作后，应遵循特定的安全规范
                            <refblock>52-10-00-860-002 
                              <refint refid="en52100086000200"> 
                                <effect effrg="001999"/>52-10-00-860-002-A
                              </refint> 
                            </refblock>。
                          </para> 
                        </l2item>  
                        <l2item> 
                          <para>Close the applicable passenger/crew door 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">831</pan> or 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">841</pan> or 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">832</pan> or 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">842</pan>  
                            <refblock>52-10-00-410-001 
                              <refint refid="en52100041000100"> 
                                <effect effrg="001999"/>52-10-00-410-001-A
                              </refint> 
                            </refblock>.
                          </para>  
                          <para lang="zh">关闭旅客/机组门 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">831</pan>或 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">841</pan>或 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">832</pan>或 
                            <pan pantype="accpan">842</pan>  
                            <refblock>52-10-00-410-001 
                              <refint refid="en52100041000100"> 
                                <effect effrg="001999"/>52-10-00-410-001-A
                              </refint> 
                            </refblock>。
                          </para> 
                        </l2item>  
                        <l2item> 
                          <para>Remove the access platform(s).</para>  
                          <para>移开接近平台。</para> 
                        </l2item> 
                      </list2> 
                    </l1item> 
